      • populateServiceDayList

        public void populateServiceDayList()
        Iterates through the Service ArrayList and counts the number of days between services. If the size of the ArrayList is 0, calls getFirstDate as the first date. If the iteration is equal to the size of the ArrayList, calls getLastDate as the second date. Uses the last service record compared to the current service record in other comparisons.
